 	<div id="main-article-info">

		
		
			<h1 itemprop="name headline  "
								>The NHS plan to share our medical data can save lives – but must be done right</h1>
		
					<div itemprop="description" id="stand-first"
				 class="stand-first-alone"                        	        data-component="Article:standfirst_cta"			>Care.data, the grand project to make the medical records of the UK population available for scientific and commercial use, is not inherently evil – far from it – but its execution has been badly bungled. Here's how the government can regain our trust</div>
		
		
  	</div>

